{"tid":1112174,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，黃心穎你條臭雞，道歉都無誠意！","createTime":"2019-04-17T09:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T11:56:16.000Z","uid":217411,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee56a09ce38dc44e25f21a1bf232be0ad7bbd1d0","tid":1112174,"uid":217411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:30:58.000Z","msg":"老鼠安都知衰拿拿聲開記者會當面鞠躬道歉，<br />\n你ig打幾句就算數？你真係無恥到極！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你對唔對得住sammi呀？佢因為你演唱會都唔知搞唔搞得成！同老鼠安五週年紀念多得你唔少喇！隨時又抑鬰症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你對唔對得住馬明呀？出曬名好仔筍盤，因為你畀人笑佢綠帽明呀！人地無做錯而因為你受恥笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n扮乜撚野受害者呀姣雞穎，話你知你有排受，你退出娛樂呀臭貨！自己負責返自己做過既野！出黎道歉！"},{"pid":"9c89118b3724e337a8deb09740b7ba15c44035d8","tid":1112174,"uid":217411,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:40:08.000Z","msg":"條臭雞一定由頭到尾都係後悔單野畀的士佬同蘋果爆出黎！"},{"pid":"fb5fbca2a69c1d3c4c68d3c5ebc73b1b0c0dc76b","tid":1112174,"uid":217411,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"臭雞！馬明宜家仲擔心你多過嬲你，你憑咩呀？<br />\n你勾引老鼠安個陣肯定當馬明傻仔喳！"},{"pid":"6cacd64b8dadd3951873b2507a2be04163a6c03f","tid":1112174,"uid":192491,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"死臭雞死番菲律賓做雞啦, 咪撚累人累物, 正臭雞"},{"pid":"6b3b2e8f89e4a06a9c28ac2505535659901ee0f6","tid":1112174,"uid":27616,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"唔開記者會，都應該拍條片，喊住口道歉，唔識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3257e8a3cb7d62236bd10ee98c489a2cc95d4587","tid":1112174,"uid":4559,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:45:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a83a9997c844710010d6c95a9f038bbbd6dabe8","tid":1112174,"uid":24989,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:46:55.000Z","msg":"其實佢都係受害者"},{"pid":"9f0416d41e274ba7487ead0f83553b